6
00:00:22,519 --> 00:00:28,550
Me neither. Better yet. How about we just start over? Clean slate.

7
00:00:28,550 --> 00:00:50,009
I don't think I heard you right.

8
00:00:50,009 --> 00:00:52,009
Stella married who?

9
00:00:52,009 --> 00:00:54,200
That bitch married my Ethan.

10
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:58,770
Same old Stella, always taking everything from me.

11
00:00:58,770 --> 00:01:01,770
This can't happen. You need to win Ethan back.

12
00:01:01,770 --> 00:01:04,769
Our company's feature depends on the Smith Group's investment.

13
00:01:04,769 --> 00:01:10,019
Am I supposed to do that, Dad? You already made me fake a pregnancy to force Ethan into a marriage with me?

14
00:01:10,019 --> 00:01:15,019
