15
00:01:15,019 --> 00:01:18,019
I'm tired of hearing excuses. Think of something.

16
00:01:18,019 --> 00:01:21,700
Or do you want to get out done by Stella again?

17
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:30,689
Speak of the devil. Look who's calling. Took him long enough.

18
00:01:30,689 --> 00:01:33,810
Work your magic, baby.

